      "lines": [
        "I WILL EARLY SEEK THE SAVIOUR"
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "chorus",
      "lines": [
        "1. Mmene ine ndiri mwana Ndzaphunzira zacezo;",
        "Ndidzamtsata Yesu yekha, M’njira ya mabvutoyo",
        "CHORUS:",
        "Inde, Yesu andikonda, Ine ndikudziwadi",
        "Kuti Yesu andikonda, Nandiferakelelo.",
